title: Nvidia Revenue Doubles on Demand for A.I. Chips, and Could Go Higher
description: Sales for the current quarter will nearly triple their total a year ago, said the company, which makes chips essential to the development of A.I. systems.

title: YouTube Improperly Used Targeted Ads on Children’s Videos, Watchdogs Say
description: One of the groups said it had used Google’s tools to run a targeted ad campaign this month on children’s channels. Google has said it did not allow such ads on videos made for children.

title: Defcon 2023: los hackers encuentran fallos de la IA
description: Los piratas informáticos actuaron con el beneplácito de la Casa Blanca y de empresas de inteligencia artificial y hallaron desinformación política, estereotipos demográficos, instrucciones para hacer vigilancia y más.
